original.text: Ever feel like your DNA is this. This total mystery novel? Like, it's full of twists and turns that you just can't decipher. Well, today we're going deep, like, really deep into the world of genomics with these AI models called Caduceus. And these models, they're getting really, really good at reading those genetic storylines.

It really is mind blowing. I mean, we're talking about AI that can, like, not only read your DNA, but also actually understand this crazy interplay of genes and then even predict how these tiny little changes could, you know, have these huge ripple effects on your health.
So rewind that for a sec, because we've got our hands on some seriously cutting edge research, like, straight.
